title: Clubs
body: It seems that I still don't have access to my personally created club, aside of the other 2 I was invited to. Could someone please help me out?

replies.body:
We can help you out if you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), since we'll need to do some investigating to see if we can resolve this.

Let me know if you have any questions.
Everyone has this problem. They are working on it...
